---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Tooltails Focus"
  description="Terms of Service for Tooltails Focus. Read our terms regarding usage, browser compatibility, and local-first data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-neutral">
      <p class="text-lg text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Welcome to Tooltails Focus. By using this timer and productivity tool, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms of Service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">1. Use of the App</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Tooltails Focus is a productivity tool provided for personal use. It focuses on helping you plan outcomes, track time, and log progress. You agree to use the application in accordance with standard browser rules and not to exploit or disrupt our services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">2. Local Data Persistence and Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Because Tooltails Focus stores data in your browser's <code class="font-mono bg-canvas-soft px-1 rounded">LocalStorage</code>, we have no capability to backup, restore, sync, or secure your goal logs or streak metrics.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You acknowledge that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-body space-y-2">
        <li>Clearing your browser cache, using private/incognito modes, or swapping devices may result in loss of your productivity data.</li>
        <li>We are not responsible for any data loss, lost streaks, or interrupted workflows caused by browser configurations, software updates, or device failures.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Tooltails Focus is provided "as is" and "as available". We do not represent or warrant that the timer, the recovery recommendations, or the audio generation will be uninterrupted, error-free, or meet all your expectations. While the sound synthesizer is designed using professional audio synthesis models, its frequency performance depends entirely on your system's soundcard and speaker setup.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">4. Updates and Changes</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We reserve the right to modify, enhance, or discontinue parts of Tooltails Focus at any time. Any changes to these terms will be updated on this page. Your continued use of the application indicates your acceptance of any revised terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
